tr.th: Conclusion and Recommendations based on this report and previous findings known to us

tr.td: All tested specific IgE antibodies are within normal limits, with no significant sensitization detected to common food or environmental allergens. No laboratory evidence of IgE-mediated allergy is present based on these results. Clinical correlation is recommended if symptoms persist.
